  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;23:14">A <systemoutput class="+ topic/ph sw-d/systemoutput " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="systemoutput:1;23:30">LookupError: Resource punkt_tab not found</systemoutput>
  error means the NLTK language data required by sentence-count or part-of-speech
  rules is not installed on your system.</shortdesc>

  <troublebody class="- topic/body troubleshooting/troublebody " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="troublebody:1;27:16">

    <condition id="condition" class="- topic/section troubleshooting/condition " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="condition:1;29:31">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="title:2;30:14">Situation</title>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="p:1;31:10">You run <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;31:26">md-validate validate</codeph> and see an error similar
      to:</p>
      <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="codeblock:1;33:39">LookupError: Resource punkt_tab not found.
Please use the NLTK Downloader to obtain the resource:
  &gt;&gt;&gt; import nltk; nltk.download('punkt_tab')</codeblock>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="p:2;36:10">This error occurs when a rule uses the <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="codeph:2;36:57">s</codeph> (sentence
      count) or <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="codeph:3;37:25">p&lt;N&gt;</codeph> (part of speech) operators and the
      required NLTK corpora are not installed.</p>
    </condition>

    <troubleSolution class="- topic/bodydiv troubleshooting/troubleSolution " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="troubleSolution:1;41:22">
      <cause id="cause" class="- topic/section troubleshooting/cause " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="cause:1;42:25">
        <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="title:3;43:16">Cause</title>
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="p:3;44:12">The NLTK language data files (<codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="codeph:4;44:50">punkt_tab</codeph> and
        <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="codeph:5;45:17">averaged_perceptron_tagger_eng</codeph>) are not included in
        the markdown-validator pip package. They must be downloaded once per
        Python environment before sentence or POS rules can run.</p>
      </cause>
      <remedy id="remedy" class="- topic/section troubleshooting/remedy " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="remedy:1;49:27">
        <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="title:4;50:16">Resolution</title>
        <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="steps:1;51:16">
          <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="step:1;52:17">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="cmd:1;53:18">Activate the virtual environment where markdown-validator is
            installed.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="info:1;55:19">
              <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="codeblock:2;56:47">source .venv/bin/activate       # macOS/Linux
.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1      # Windows PowerShell</codeblock>
            </info>
          </step>
          <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="step:2;60:17">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="cmd:2;61:18">Download the required NLTK corpora.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="info:2;62:19">
              <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="codeblock:3;63:47">python -m nltk.downloader punkt_tab averaged_perceptron_tagger_eng</codeblock>
            </info>
            <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="stepresult:1;65:25">NLTK downloads the files to your NLTK data directory
            (<filepath class="+ topic/ph sw-d/filepath " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="filepath:1;66:24">~/nltk_data</filepath> on macOS/Linux).</stepresult>
          </step>
          <step class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/troubleshooting/ts_nltk-error.dita" xtrc="step:3;68:17">
